# SpriteRenderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Render bridge for world-space sprites: sole adder of DrawSpriteInFrameEvent. Each frame it emits
one in-frame draw event per SpriteComponent, building a sprite from the component's transform,
sub-texture rectangle, texture id and origin.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SpriteComponent | read | One draw event emitted per sprite |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DrawSpriteInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One per SpriteComponent; consumed by Renderer2DSystem this frame |
